thread.title: Asian Shares Lower After Wall Street Fades

author: Kenan Machado
title: Asian Shares Lower After Wall Street Fades
text:
Goldman Sachs, Bank of America report results Dow poised for all-time high Euro falls after ECB comments U.S. stocks were on track for fresh records Wednesday following a spate of bank earnings, even as markets in Europe and Asia largely stalled.
Futures pointed to a 0.4% opening rise for the Dow Jones Industrial Average after it briefly climbed above the 26000 milestone on Tuesday before giving up gains.
